(1036, 218, 'description', '<ol>\r\n 	<li>Can be used in household or office building parking lot.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dual-cylinder lifting system, more stable.</li>\r\n 	<li>Connecting shaft to make sure synchronous balancing,</li>\r\n 	<li>Low height post, faster lifting speed.</li>\r\n 	<li>Platform angle adjustable, can be used in low ceiling shop.</li>\r\n 	<li>Single manual- lock release system, safe and reliable.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mold machining through the whole process so that the parts are universal and interchangeable</li>\r\n 	<li>Pass 120% capacity dynamic load text and 150% static load test.</li>\r\n 	<li>Italian oil seal to make sure no oil leakage</li>\r\n 	<li>Solenoid valve has the urgent manual lock release function.</li>\r\n 	<li>Optional manual pump on power unit in case of power off.</li>\r\n 	<li>Optional 24v control box, solenoid value.</li>\r\n 	<li>Optional ultrared rays alarm device, in case of unguarded entrance.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
