(2559, 359, 'product_content_0_content', '<strong>Pressure, Temperature, Voltage, Current and Process</strong>\r\n\r\nCircular chart recorders are available in 3 different sizes of the charts i.e. 4, 6 and 11. The 11 chart recorder is very useful when you want to monitor your process unattended.\r\n\r\nThese recorders are widely used in process industry for monitoring of various processes like incubation, curing, pasteurization etc. It takes direct input from RTD Pt-100 / Thermocouples / process inputs like 4-20mA / 0-20mA / 0-1V. These recorders are microcontroller based. Crystal controlled chart drive ensures accurate chart speed. Stepper motors for both pens and chart drive, ensures no lag and no backlash.\r\n\r\nA panel cut-out of 319323 mm makes it a perfect fit for replacing any of your existing recorders of any make. Transparent polycarbonate door window makes the chart visible from the distance. They come with universal power supply as a standard feature. Other power supply inputs are also available.'),
