(2577, 362, 'features', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Mercury Free or Mercury Filled Temperature Systems Available</li>\r\n 	<li>Crush Resistant, and Dust-proof</li>\r\n 	<li>Easy Open Double Throw Latches</li>\r\n 	<li>Open cell core with solid wall design  strong and light weight</li>\r\n 	<li>Automatic Pressure Equalization Valve</li>\r\n 	<li>Comfortable rubber over-molded handle</li>\r\n 	<li>Stainless Steel hardware and padlock protectors</li>\r\n 	<li>Heavy Duty Deflector Ribs</li>\r\n 	<li>Carefully heat treated coil provides superior spring action</li>\r\n 	<li>Durable, low maintenance design: thermal system and other parts easily replaced by field technician</li>\r\n 	<li>300 Series stainless steel bulb and interconnection capillary, with armor protection available on certain designs</li>\r\n 	<li>Standard case compensated system for uncompensated capillary</li>\r\n 	<li>lengths not exceeding 25</li>\r\n 	<li>All 316 Stainless Steel Pressure Elements</li>\r\n 	<li>The Pelican Case is also available in six colours.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
