(2759, 385, 'features', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Selectable Stems, Rigid, All Angle and Remote  Large 1 LCD Continuous Display</li>\r\n 	<li>Easy to Read from Over 20 Ft.  Battery Operated</li>\r\n 	<li>Meter Accuracies from  0.3F ( 0.2C)  Factory Calibration Lot Traceable to NIST (Optional)</li>\r\n 	<li>Direct Replacement for Bimetal, Mercury-in-Glass, Bulb &amp; Capillary Thermometers</li>\r\n 	<li>Temperature Ranges from -328 to 1472F (-200 to 800C)  Easy to Install</li>\r\n 	<li>NEMA-4X Stainless Housing  Hose-Down Proof, Vibration Tolerant</li>\r\n 	<li>Optional RTD or Thermocouple Output  4-20 mA Transmitter with Local Display, Loop Power</li>\r\n</ul>'),
