(308, 1, '2021-06-17 10:53:21', '2021-06-17 04:23:21', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prefabrication, installation and maintenance of piping systems for industry. With professional disassembly and on-site surveys, we achieve the best possible basis for true to dimension production and professional installation of piping Systems pipe supports (supports, sliding carriages and brackets), secondary supports and custom-made products such as double wall pipe systems. Profound know-how in handing different materials and dimensions distinguishes us. Our treasure trove of experience ranges from simple to high-alloy steel and also includes plastics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We ensure the capability of the installed piping system using pressure tests and acceptance. The installation of equipment and instruments is also a part of our services, if required. Our experienced engineers, technicians, construction site managers, service engineers and fitters provide a smooth construction site workflow and an on-time order execution for projects of different sizes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We support you during commissioning and undertake the technical documentation for you. Naturally, we also support you long-term in the field of maintenance and servicing. If required, our engineering partners can take on the complete planning and design of the required systems in advance of the production and Installation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Piping & Steel Work Installation', 'Prefabrication, installation and maintenance', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'piping-steel-work-installation', '', '', '2021-06-17 10:55:45', '2021-06-17 04:25:45', '', 0, 'http://mr-provider.b360/?post_type=service&#038;p=308', 0, 'service', '', 0),
